Class StudentGradeData

java.lang.Object
comp3111.examsystem.tools.Entity
comp3111.examsystem.entity.StudentGradeData
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<Entity>
public class StudentGradeData extends Entity
Represents the grade data for a student in the examination system. This class encapsulates information about the student's performance in a specific exam, including their scores and the time spent on the exam.
